---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us">
  <section class="text-center mb-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-[var(--color-secondary)] mb-4">About Car Rentals</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">We are passionate about making your journey comfortable, safe, and memorable. Our story is one of innovation, dedication, and a love for the open road.</p>
  </section>
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-20 bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-8">
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-secondary)] mb-4">Our Story</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Founded in 2022, Car Rentals began as a small family business with a big dream: to make car rentals easy, affordable, and enjoyable for everyone. Over the years, we've grown into a trusted provider with a diverse fleet and a commitment to customer satisfaction. Our journey is fueled by our customers' adventures and the memories they create on the road.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">From city commutes to cross-country road trips, we believe every journey should be special. That's why we focus on quality, transparency, and service excellence in everything we do.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex justify-center">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503736334956-4c8f8e92946d?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="About us placeholder" class="rounded-2xl shadow-md w-full max-w-xs md:max-w-sm object-cover" />
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-20">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-secondary)] mb-8 text-center">Our Values</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow p-6 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
        <div class="bg-[var(--color-primary)]/10 text-[var(--color-primary)] rounded-full p-4 mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Customer First</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">We put our customers at the heart of everything we do, ensuring a seamless and enjoyable experience.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow p-6 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
        <div class="bg-[var(--color-primary)]/10 text-[var(--color-primary)] rounded-full p-4 mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M12 20a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Integrity & Transparency</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">We believe in honesty and openness, building trust through clear communication and fair practices.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow p-6 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
        <div class="bg-[var(--color-primary)]/10 text-[var(--color-primary)] rounded-full p-4 mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Innovation</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">We embrace new ideas and technologies to continually improve our services and exceed expectations.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow p-6 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
        <div class="bg-[var(--color-primary)]/10 text-[var(--color-primary)] rounded-full p-4 mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 20h5v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87M9 20H4v-2a4 4 0 013-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75M8 3.13a4 4 0 000 7.75" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Reliability</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Count on us for dependable vehicles and consistent, high-quality service every time you rent.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow p-6 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
        <div class="bg-[var(--color-primary)]/10 text-[var(--color-primary)] rounded-full p-4 mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 1.343-3 3s1.343 3 3 3 3-1.343 3-3-1.343-3-3-3zm0 0V4m0 8v8" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Passion for Travel</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">We love the open road and are dedicated to helping you explore it with comfort and confidence.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout> 